sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KubeRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as OVMS REST Server<br/>(Drogon HTTP)<br/>configurable/TCP
    participant GRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>(HTTP/2)<br/>configurable/TCP
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler
    participant MediaPipe as MediaPipe Graph<br/>Executor
    participant ModelMgr as ModelManager
    participant ModelInst as ModelInstance
    participant CBPipeline as ContinuousBatching<br/>Pipeline
    participant OVRuntime as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>2026.0
    participant OVGenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>2026.0
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (KServe v2)
    Client->>KubeRBAC: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: K8s Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KubeRBAC->>REST: Forward (HTTP localhost)<br/>Token validated via TokenReview
    REST->>Handler: Route to KServe v2 handler
    Handler->>ModelMgr: getModelInstance(model, version)
    ModelMgr->>ModelInst: infer(request)
    ModelInst->>OVRuntime: InferRequest::infer()
    OVRuntime-->>ModelInst: Inference result (tensors)
    ModelInst-->>Handler: Inference response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>KubeRBAC: HTTP 200 OK
    KubeRBAC-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completions (Streaming SSE)
    Client->>REST: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API key (optional)<br/>stream: true
    REST->>Handler: Route to OpenAI v3 handler
    Handler->>Handler: isAuthorized() check API key
    Handler->>MediaPipe: Execute LLM calculator graph
    MediaPipe->>CBPipeline: Schedule generation request
    loop Continuous Batching (token by token)
        CBPipeline->>OVGenAI: Generate next token(s)
        OVGenAI-->>CBPipeline: Token(s)
        CBPipeline-->>MediaPipe: Token callback
        MediaPipe-->>Handler: Partial response
        Handler-->>REST: SSE data chunk
        REST-->>Client: text/event-stream chunk
    end
    REST-->>Client: SSE [DONE]

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: gRPC Inference (KServe ModelInfer)
    Client->>GRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC (HTTP/2)<br/>InsecureServerCredentials
    GRPC->>ModelMgr: getModelInstance(model, version)
    ModelMgr->>ModelInst: infer(request)
    ModelInst->>OVRuntime: InferRequest::infer()
    OVRuntime-->>ModelInst: Inference result
    ModelInst-->>GRPC: InferResponse protobuf
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    ModelMgr->>ModelMgr: Config watcher thread<br/>(poll interval: file_system_poll_wait_seconds)
    ModelMgr->>S3: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: IAM/ServiceAccount/ConnString<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>ModelMgr: Model files (binary)
    ModelMgr->>ModelMgr: Write to local cache
    ModelMgr->>OVRuntime: Core::compile_model()
    OVRuntime-->>ModelMgr: Compiled model ready
    ModelMgr->>ModelMgr: Update model version map
